{"id":88164,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/吉林永吉遭遇1600年不遇水灾，死亡人数无法估计（/","date":"2010-08-02T13:12:25Z","modified":"2010-08-02T13:12:25Z","title":"吉林永吉遭遇1600年不遇水灾，死亡人数无法估计（高清组图）","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/1078809/2\">3P女王雷囧水俱乐部 – Mtime时光网 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月01日,  已有 6 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<div>（转自网络）</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>我擦，今天才知道这事</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714706/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165753.74939976_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>连日来，吉林省普降暴雨，松花江上游洪水暴涨。27日20时至28日12时，永吉县平均降雨量达120.7毫米，达到大暴雨标准。其中，永吉县官厅乡降雨量254.9毫米，为特大暴雨。此次强降雨直接导致饮马河流域的金家乡、温德河流域的口前镇、松花江支流漂尔河的旺起镇等一些乡镇遭受洪灾。据水利部门测算，其中温德河为有水文记录以来最大洪水，口前水文站为1600年一遇洪水。</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714709/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165755.18810456_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714708/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165755.63150837_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714707/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714707/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165755.43015129_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714707/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714702/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165752.60233427_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714702/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714703/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165752.30461243_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714703/\"></a></div>\n</div>\n<hr color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"2\">\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714705/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165753.17715741_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714705/\"></a>整个县城交通、供水、供电、通讯全部瘫痪。房屋倒塌无数，死亡人数目前尚无法统计。“我活了80来岁了，从未见过这么大的水。”昨日，永吉县县城一位王老先生这样告诉记者。</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>1600年不遇，你活1600岁也见不到这么大的水！</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img21.mtime.cn/mg/2010/08/01/170130.30538158.jpg\" /></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img21.mtime.cn/mg/2010/08/01/170208.77543738.jpg\" /></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img21.mtime.cn/mg/2010/08/01/170214.73574570.jpg\" /></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<hr color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"2\">\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>　货运列车被冲出数百米</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>　　昨日上午9时许，通往永吉县、磐石市、桦甸市的最直接的通道吉林市温德河大桥由于温德河水位迅速上涨，流量非常大，同时有洪峰要通过，加上该桥又是危桥，所以吉林市封闭了该桥。而吉林市的外环也被封闭，这样使得吉林市通往永吉、桦甸、磐石的大型车辆等一切交通基本上隔绝，小车只能绕到丰满大桥通行。而丰满大桥也是危桥，被限定只能轿车以下的车辆通行，13时30分许，记者看到，该危桥的限高正在被有关部门去除，以方便大车通行。下午6时，建成后一直未投入使用的蓝旗大桥也开始有小型车辆通行，而坊间流传该桥一直未通过验收。</div>\n<div>　　28日7时，吉林市境内两处水库溃堤，致使永吉县城遭遇罕见内涝灾害，就在现场，一列货运列车被冲出数百米，20余节车厢被掀翻；水位最高处达18.7米，沿街淤泥达1米多深，数百栋民宅被淹至没顶，部分低矮民房被冲垮。沈阳军区某红军师闻讯紧急出动千余名官兵赶赴现场，目前救援工作正在紧张进行。</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714701/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165751.29596647_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714700/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165751.13253490_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714699/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714699/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165750.21190569_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714699/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714698/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165750.61747531_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714698/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714694/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165745.81842660_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714694/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714695/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165746.34734199_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714695/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714696/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165747.17488823_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714696/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714697/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165749.87374658_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714697/\"></a></div>\n<hr color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"2\">\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>汽车上了房 遇水翻滚</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>　　永吉县城到处都是被水冲走的汽车，有的汽车撞到电线杆上翻了个；有的汽车玩起了“杂技”，折叠在一起；有的侧翻在马路上；有的陷进污泥内；有的躲进“草从”中；有的顶牛在一起。据一位参与救援的永吉县政府一位官员讲，当时他们营救被困居民，水突然上涨，他看见，一些正在开车的或停在路上的轿车像风吹落叶般翻滚，车内很多人都没出来，就被洪水卷走了。因此，此次洪水肯定造成了人员伤亡。一位灾民告诉记者，他看到，一些轿车根本不用开，在水上像船一样荡来荡去的。</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714690/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165743.68179823_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714690/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714691/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165743.70798907_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714691/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714692/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165744.59353073_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714692/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714693/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165745.66560134_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714693/\"></a></div>\n<hr color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"2\">\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>“水上房”成了“拦路虎”</div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>　　在采访中，记者听到更多的是关于“水上房”的抱怨。从一些商家口中记者得知，他们所说的“水上房”是指建在四间河桥与口桦公路交会路口处，即紧挨客运站旁的四间河上的两处二层商品楼，这两处商品楼分别建在四间河桥的两侧。百姓们称，这两处商品楼成了巨大的阻水障碍物，记者看到，在该桥的上游处，由于该商品楼的挡水，一些玉米秆插在了商品楼的底部，导致洪水改变水流方向，直接上了岸，将岸边的道路冲刷开一道口子，一些玉米和上游冲刷下来的漂浮物滞留在那里，旁边的一些商家说，他们那里受灾要比其他的地方严重，就是因为这个“阻水商品楼”导致水在他们那里积蓄抬升，给他们造成了巨大的损失。</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714689/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165742.63126288_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714689/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714688/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165742.45042999_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714688/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714687/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165741.74638192_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714687/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714686/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165741.81282324_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714686/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714682/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165739.96664288_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714682/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714683/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165739.12795733_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714683/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714684/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165740.58635777_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714684/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714685/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165740.44205784_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<hr color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"2\">\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714685/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714681/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165738.19530815_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714681/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714680/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165738.64775492_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714680/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714679/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165738.40034996_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714679/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714678/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165737.73515692_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714678/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714673/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165735.61995351_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714673/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714674/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165736.74106578_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714674/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714675/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165736.83418709_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714675/\"><span></span></a><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714676/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/01/165737.97720915_500.jpg\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3714676/\"></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://group.mtime.com/queen/discussion/1161259\" title=\"吉林永吉遭遇1600年不遇水灾，死亡人数无法估计（高清组图）\">吉林永吉遭遇1600年不遇水灾，死亡人数无法估计（高清组图）</a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}